opendoc
Copyright 2026 arcships

This product embeds lark-cli (github.com/larksuite/cli, MIT License) as a
compiled-in Go module: the hidden `opendoc lark-engine` subcommand dispatches
into it in-process, so lark-cli's code is distributed as part of the opendoc
binary. Other third-party Go module dependencies compiled into release
binaries are listed in go.mod with their own licenses.
